Title: Connexxus/Centro de Mujeres Collection, 1985-1991
Description.abstract: The Connexxus/Centro de Mujeres Collection contains the administrative records of Connexxus / Centro de Mujeres, one of the first Los Angeles non-profit organizations that catered and provided services to lesbians.
